snippet.title: Claws & Chaos Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Claws & Chaos is an auto-chess-style battler from Parhelion Studio featuring charming creatures in dire circumstances. Build your team and hone your skills while battling across both story and competitive PvP modes. 

Join the community at https://discord.gg/clawsnchaos!
